Quickstrike:




"Ah'm okay now." Quickstrike said to Stingtra. Megatron was making him 
nervous. He made it clear to himself not to go near him today. He knew 
better than to get too close. Megatron had a loose fuse.

He hear the female scorpion say she wanted to go to the lake, now going to 
the mouth of the cave. That sparked danager in his mind. He ran to her and 
grabbed her arm. "Wait!" he said. "Ah don't reckon that ain't the best idea. 
Remember what ah said? Don't go alone."
